Package: BioTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools based on Biostrings (alignment, classification, database)
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 20xx-xx-xx
Author:  Michael Hahsler and Anurag Nagar
Maintainer: Michael Hahsler <mhahsler@lyle.smu.edu>, Anurag Nagar <andynagar@yahoo.com>
Description: Interfaces several popular tools for sequence alignment (clustalw, kalign), data base search (BLAST) and classification (RDP). Also provides a database to manage 16S rRNA sequences. Based on Biostrings (from Bioconductor). This work is supported by grant no. R21HG005912 from the National Human Genome Research Institute.
Depends: Biostrings (>= 2.26.2), DBI, RSQLite, seqLogo, proxy
SystemRequirements: rdp-classifier, clustalw, kalign, ncbi-blast+
Enhances: Biostrings
License: GPL-2
